{
  "stem": "766.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he remained to study his-- his subject.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did it myself, with a-- a colleague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember how we got together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went to Rouen too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And over there we moved into a-- also a hotel, where already recommended us that they are already Polish student, and they're from-- were even from Russia, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we moved in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we started and this for a whole year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in Nancy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't move at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the oldest, was nine years older.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he finished the Russian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because at that time when he entered school, were no Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in the Russian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he finished in 1916, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went, again, as-- he went for year to the polytechnic in Warsaw, to study engineering.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was there-- this was-- that time was not yet independence of Poland, 1916.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think after a-- a year or-- or two-- I don't remember, I was too young-- for which reason probably it wasn't good enough, the-- the polytechnic, I don't know-- he went to study in Prague, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at the time when I-- when he finished, he couldn't return to Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he also was not a citizen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they blamed him that there-- when-- when there was the War of Independence in Poland, the war with Russia, after the end of the First World War, He was sitting in-- in Prague and studying when they were fighting on fronts.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was partly a punishment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And partly he wasn't a citizenship-- a citizen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he couldn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in Prague, he had a hard time because he had no right to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
